<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Our Services - Sweet Crumbs Cake Bakery</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="inner-page">
  <header class="bakery-header">
    <button class="menu-button" aria-label="Open menu">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </button>
    <a href="/" class="bakery-logo">
      <span class="logo-mark">BAKERY</span>
      <span class="logo-subtitle">Sweet Crumbs</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="bakery-nav">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/services" class="active">Our Services</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="/contact" class="outline-button">Order Now</a>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="inner-hero services-hero">
      <div>
        <p class="section-kicker">Made with care</p>
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Elegant cakes, soft pastries, and custom dessert tables for your sweetest moments.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="elegant-section">
      <div class="services-grid elegant-grid">
        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">01</span>
          <h3>Birthday Cakes</h3>
          <p>Colorful buttercream cakes with custom names, themes, candles, and soft decoration.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">02</span>
          <h3>Wedding Cakes</h3>
          <p>Tiered cakes with refined florals, delicate textures, and classic bakery flavors.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">03</span>
          <h3>Cupcake Boxes</h3>
          <p>Assorted cupcakes for parties, family gifts, baby showers, and office events.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">04</span>
          <h3>Dessert Tables</h3>
          <p>Mini cakes, cake pops, brownies, cookies, and small sweets arranged beautifully.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">05</span>
          <h3>Custom Flavors</h3>
          <p>Choose sponge, cream, fruit, chocolate, frosting, and toppings for your own cake.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="service-item elegant-card">
          <span class="service-number">06</span>
          <h3>Pre-Order Pickup</h3>
          <p>Schedule your order during working hours and collect it fresh from the bakery.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="elegant-cta">
        <h2>Need a cake this week?</h2>
        <p>Send us your event date and guest count, and we will suggest the perfect size.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn dark-btn">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a href="/" class="footer-logo">Sweet Crumbs</a>
    <p>Fresh cakes, pastries, and dessert tables for elegant celebrations.</p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"></rect><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1"></circle></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 8h3V4h-3c-3 0-5 2-5 5v3H6v4h3v5h4v-5h3l1-4h-4V9c0-.6.4-1 1-1z"></path></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Snapchat">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3c3 0 5 2.4 5 5.6v2.1c0 1.4 1.3 2.2 2.6 2.6-.6 1.5-2 2.3-3.6 2.5-.7 1.5-2 2.2-4 2.2s-3.3-.7-4-2.2c-1.6-.2-3-.9-3.6-2.5 1.3-.4 2.6-1.2 2.6-2.6V8.6C7 5.4 9 3 12 3z"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <small>&copy; 2026 Sweet Crumbs Cake Bakery. Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 5 PM.</small>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
